title: Silver 3, Support Main LF a team or whatever
body:
I'm a silver support main, peaked G2 in season 4 before I took a year break. I'm back and looking to climb. Feel free to check out my match history, I do really, really well in a team. I'm looking to climb as fast as I can.

HIt me up, IGN: AlphaCueSlowly

Teamspeak would be preferred, thank you!
